headline: What Makes Rockwell Automation (ROK) a High-Quality Compounder?
summary: Alpha Wealth Funds, LLC, an investment management company, released its Q3 2025 letter for the “Insiders Fund”. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund returned 4.96% in September, bringing the YTD returns to 21.37%. This compares to the benchmark, S&P 500 September return of 3.65% and the year-to-date return through September […]
